<p>Losing a pet is like losing a member of the family.  These messages aim to acknowledge the deep connection and offer comfort to grieving families.</p>
<li>My heart goes out to you all during this difficult time.</li>
<li>Thinking of you and sending love during your loss.</li>
<li>Your pet held a special place in your hearts, and their memory will live on.</li>
<li>We were so sorry to hear about the passing of your beloved pet.</li>
<li> [Pet's name] was such a special animal; they'll be deeply missed.</li>
<li>Sending you strength and comfort as you grieve.</li>
<li>May warm memories bring you solace in the days to come.</li>
